    "client_msg_id": "15f48ab9-33a0-477b-a296-5ca6652053f8",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "More broadly, I don’t think there’s a comprehensive model of cognition in arbitrary software maintenance tasks, particularly for software in 2020. So if your goal is to design an IDE for improving code comprehension, you’ll want to get as specific as possible to find related work.",
